BUILD Instructions
------------------
(1) Ensure that libcurl (v7.13.1 preferrably) is installed on the system
(libcurl must be downloaded and installed separately and is not distributed
with this package.)

(2)Ensure the libtools is installed on your system. Then execute 
# ./bootstrap

(3) Execute configure to generate the Makefiles
# ./configure

(4) Execute "make" to build the files
# make

(5) Do a "make install" to install the headers and the libraries 
# make install 
